""" Image - rotate - rgb,negative degree """
image = Image('files/1_100.jpg', 1, config=['resize=(64,64)'])
rotated = image.rotate(-30)
self.assertTrue(rotated.shape, (64, 64))
rotated = image.rotate(-45)
self.assertTrue(rotated.shape, (64, 64))
rotated = image.rotate(-60)
self.assertTrue(rotated.shape, (64, 64))
